description:
Capture takes care of your memories!

- Back up photos and videos safely in Capture. Even if you lose your phone, your photos are safe in the cloud.
- Free up space on your phone - never worry about full phone storage again!
- Shared albums let you and your friends share photos in the same album - the easiest way to share photos from travels or parties!

Features and benefits of Capture:

FREE PHOTO STORAGE
Everyone who downloads Capture gets minimum 2 GB free storage for photos and videos. 

If you are a Telenor customer you may have more storage included in your subscription. Check with your local provider if you are entitled to more storage!

When your photos are backed up in Capture, you have access to them on all your devices. The photos are only visible to you, and they are safely stored.


FREE UP SPACE ON YOUR PHONE 
All photos and videos which are uploaded to Capture are safely stored. 
With the click of a button, you can find photos and videos that are safely stored in Capture, and delete them from your phone.
You are in total control, but weâ€™ll do the heavy lifting for you.


ALBUM - PHOTO SHARING MADE SIMPLE!
Shared albums let you and your friends share photos in the same album - the easiest way to share photos from travels or parties without having to publish them on Facebook or send them one by one. Keep all your memories in one place. 

You can also create albums to organise your own photos, and share the album when you want and with whomever you want. 

SAFE AND SECURE
Your privacy is our highest priority.

Photos and videos are only available to you. You choose what photos you want to share - and with whom.

EASY TO USE
Your photos are automatically uploaded if you enable this in the app. 

Capture automatically saves a backup of your photos, making them safe no matter what happens to your phone.

FULL QUALITY PHOTOS
We never compress your photos. Photos and videos will always be saved at full resolution and quality.

ACCESS YOUR PHOTOS ON ANY DEVICE
No matter what device you use or where you are, you can always access your photos in Capture. Simply download Capture to the device and all your memories are right there at your fingertips.


----------------------------------------

We offer 2 GB free storage to all users. If you are a Telenor customer you may have more storage included in your subscription. Check with your local provider if you are entitled to more storage. 

In App Purchase:
You can purchase more storage in Capture if needed via yearly or monthly plans. These are the available plans:

10 GB extra storage - available for yearly or monthly subscription.
25 GB extra storage - available for yearly or monthly subscription.
100 GB extra storage - available for yearly or monthly subscription.

You can choose packages of 10 GB, 25 GB or 100 GB storage, and pay either on an annual or a monthly basis.

Payment will be charged to your iTunes account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the iTunes Store after purchase. The current Capture storage package price starts at $1.49 USD per month. Prices are in US dollars, may vary in countries other than the US, and are subject to change without notice. Subscriptions are available on a monthly or annual basis. No cancellation of current subscriptions is allowed during the active subscription period.
